{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 We\u8217're living in a time where knowing how to effectively interact with AI is crucial to harnessing its full potential.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 1.\tx360\tab Ask the right questions.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 2.\tx360\tab Give the right hints.\par}
