{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Practical AI mastering tips\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Problem}: AI provides subpar solutions or fails to resolve the issue.\line {\b Solution}: Ask AI, \u8220"What specific information or data is needed to fix this problem?\u8221"\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Problem}: AI stumbles on multi-layered tasks requiring decomposition into manageable steps.\line {\b Solution}: Hint AI, \u8220"Please break down this problem into a series of step-by-step actions.\u8221"\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Problem}: AI lacks understanding of the project\u8217's core or file system layout.\line {\b Solution}: Create WIKI page with project overview, its structure, and aims. Hint AI:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \u8220"Analyze this project documentation at:\u8221" - https://company.com/solution/wiki/home.md - C:.wiki.md\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Problem}: AI develops solutions that don\u8217't align with the environment or project technology stack.\line {\b Solution}: Hint AI:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \u8220"Analyze these resources for a bespoke solution:\u8221" - Solution File: C:.Solution.sln - Project File: C:.Solution.Project.csproj - Coding Standards: C:.editorconfig\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Problem}: AI generates code that\u8217's hard to understand or maintain.\line {\b Solution}: Supply AI with examples of well-documented company code from previous projects. Hint AI:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \u8220"Refer to these examples of clean and well-documented code for crafting your solution:\u8221" - Repository Link: https://company.com/solution/repo/clean-code-examples - Local Directory: C:-code-examples\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Problem}: AI generates code suggestions that do not match the current code.\line {\b Solution}: Provide AI with multiple relevant files.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Hint AI in VS Extension: \u8220"Analyze all open documents.\u8221"\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Hint AI in Application: \u8220"Analyze all of these files:\u8221"\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab UI: C:.xaml\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab Code: C:.xaml.cs\sa180\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Problem}: The AI generates generic and self-explanatory code comments.\line {\b Solution}: To improve the quality of comments, follow these steps:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 1.\tx360\tab Enable the {\f1 GetSelection} and {\f1 GetOpenDocuments} functions on the {\f1 [Plugins]\\[VisualStudio]} tab in Visual Studio.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 2.\tx360\tab Open the relevant files in Visual Studio.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 3.\tx360\tab Select the code block that you want to comment.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 4.\tx360\tab Paste the prompt below and click the \u8220"Send\u8221" button.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \f1 Task 1:\line
\line
   Get current selection. Get open documents.\line
\line
Task 2:\line
\line
   a) Analyze the selected code block within the open documents.\line
\line
   b) Determine the business context of the code.\line
\line
   c) Comment directly on the selected code block, focusing on the underlying business logic and its interactions with other system components. Ensure comments are insightful, avoiding the explanation of self-evident technical details. Comments must be clear, succinct, and free of superfluous technical terms.\line
\line
   d) Output the updated selection with the newly added comments.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Note: This request may slow down the response time of the AI and incur higher costs, depending on the size of the relevant files\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 GPT-4 Issues\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Problem}: The AI only processes the beginning of the file when the input context is large.\line {\b Solution}: Hint AI, \u8220"Analyze the entire file until the end.\u8221"\par}
